## Hard stops — Design sync (design TSX ↔ production)

Design workflows are **not set up** in this repo yet.

When asked to **sync designs**, **sync all designs**, **review Designs**, or **implement from a design draft**:

1. Ask the user where the design drafts/runtime live for this repo.
2. Treat any design execution as **local-only** until the design playbooks and commands exist (STOP if you would otherwise run `bun run designs:sync`).

